creator: AppQuik
descriptionHtml:
The Vet Pal is an android app that allows large animal veterinarians record Tuberculosis skin tests, clinical information, and animal treatments on a durable, waterproof handheld device.
The app can work offline allowing the vets to use the app when in a farm setting. The app is designed to allow data to be easily inputted using either a touchscreen or a keypad enabled device.
descriptionShort: The Vet Pal app is specifically designed for farm animal veterinarians
